From 3320378f091f29729035d4f28b0f9a982d230fc4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: RCA Agent <agent@arena.ai>
Date: Sun, 7 Jun 2026 15:20:58 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] feat(export): add PDF export alongside DOCX
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- pdf_export_service.generate_pdf(result) via fpdf2; mirrors DOCX layout
  (header+meta, summary, causal/bowtie sections, recommendations table,
  technical info) with the same color palette
- bundle DejaVuSans TTF fonts (src/services/fonts/) for Cyrillic — works in
  Docker without system fonts
- export route: GET /results/{id}/export?format=docx|pdf (default docx,
  backward compatible); invalid format -> 422
- frontend: api.exportResult(id, methodology, format); ⬇️ DOCX + ⬇️ PDF buttons
- add fpdf2 to dependencies; gitignore frontend/dist
- tests/unit/test_pdf_export_service.py (8 tests, all methodologies + edge cases)
- README + docs/state.md updated (PDF export done)
---
